Robert BURRELL, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 7786. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. March 15, 1938. H. R. Ratcliff, of Memphis, Tenn., for appellant. William McClanahan, U. S. Atty., of Memphis, Tenn.

Before HICKS, SIMONS, and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

No reversible error appearing upon the record, it is hereby ordered and adjudged that the judgment appealed from be, and the same is in all things, affirmed.
